---
import "../styles/global.css";
import Baselayout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Socials from "../components/Social.astro";
---

<Baselayout>
  <section class="flex flex-col gap-6 text-zinc-300">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
      <h1 class="text-xl font-medium tracking-tight text-zinc-100">
        Parthiv Saikia
      </h1>

      <p class="text-[16px] leading-8">
        Building backend systems, terminal interfaces, and local-first software
        using Go and Zig.
      </p>
    </div>

    <section class="flex flex-col gap-4 text-[16px] leading-8">
      <p>
        Most of my interests orbit around Linux, Kubernetes, Docker, cloud
        native tooling, and software that stays out of the way. Currently
        building
        <a
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          href="https://github.com/parthivsaikia/enmasec"
          class="underline decoration-1 underline-offset-4 decoration-zinc-600 hover:decoration-zinc-300 transition-colors duration-200"
        >
          Enmasec
          <span class="text-sm opacity-70">↗</span>
        </a>, a local-first TUI password manager.
      </p>

      <p>
        I enjoy tools that feel fast, calm, and durable over time. Lately I’ve
        been exploring terminal UI design, distributed systems, and simpler ways
        to interact with software. You can find more about the tools, setups,
        and software I currently use on the
        <a
          href="/use"
          class="underline decoration-1 underline-offset-4 decoration-zinc-600 hover:decoration-zinc-300 transition-colors duration-200"
        >
          uses
        </a>
        page.
      </p>

      <p>
        Outside of coding, I read books, watch far too many programming videos,
        explore anime, rice my Linux setup, try new TUIs, and occasionally spend
        an unreasonable amount of time optimizing Neovim for microscopic
        performance gains. I also keep a small
        <a
          href="/now"
          class="underline decoration-1 underline-offset-4 decoration-zinc-600 hover:decoration-zinc-300 transition-colors duration-200"
        >
          now
        </a>
        page for things I’m currently doing, learning, watching, and building.
      </p>
    </section>
  </section>

  <section class="flex flex-col gap-3 pt-2 text-zinc-300">
    <p class="text-sm">Find me on</p>
    <Socials />
  </section>
</Baselayout>
